    <article>
      <h1>What Is ChargeKr?</h1>
      <p>ChargeKr is an EV charger discovery and charger-sharing app for India. It helps EV users find nearby chargers and allows charger owners to list charging points.</p>

      <section>
        <h2>How does ChargeKR work?</h2>
        <p>ChargeKR helps users search for nearby charger listings, view details, get directions and book or schedule charging where available.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Who is ChargeKR for?</h2>
        <p>Electric two-wheeler and four-wheeler owners, daily commuters, road-trip planners and charger owners who want to share chargers.</p>
      </section>

      <p><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chargekr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download ChargeKr on Android</a></p>
    </article>
